      "updated": 1770580587333,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Undirected (summetric matrix - mirrored across diagonal A^\\top = A)\nDirected\n\nHow to store\nAdjacency Matrix\nAdjacency List\n\nWeighted\nUnweighted\n\nStore graphs in adjacency lists\nUse them for math with adjacency matrix\n\nDegree = Max going out edges \n(for 1 node specifically) in a graph",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Undirected (summetric matrix - mirrored across diagonal A^\\top = A)\nDirected\n\nHow to store\nAdjacency Matrix\nAdjacency List\n\nWeighted\nUnweighted\n\nStore graphs in adjacency lists\nUse them for math with adjacency matrix\n\nDegree = Max going out edges \n(for 1 node specifically) in a graph",
