      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Any ud graph of N nodes,\nmax number of edges would\nbe => E = (N-1)^2\n\nIf we have a complete graph\nwith E edges, how many nodes\nwould there be sqrt(E) + 1 = N",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Any ud graph of N nodes,\nmax number of edges would\nbe => E = (N-1)^2\n\nIf we have a complete graph\nwith E edges, how many nodes\nwould there be sqrt(E) + 1 = N",
